    <div class="mx-auto max-w-prose">
      <H>about me</H>
      <p class="mb-8">
        I'm a student from Las Vegas, Nevada who's been interested in computers
        and technology all my life, as well as music, camping, soccer, and
        games.
        <br />
        I am currently attending Oregon State University getting a degree in Electrical
        and Computer Engineering.
        <br />
        In my free time I like to listen to music (Radiohead fanboy), play guitar,
        watch movies (go see Baby Driver), and play video games.
      </p>

      <H>platforms</H>
      <div class="mt-1 mb-8 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <Social name="github" link="github.com/BEnh3N" />
        <Social name="bluesky" link="bsky.app/profile/benh3n.com" />
        <Social name="youtube" link="youtube.com/@BEnh3N" />
        <Social name="linkedin" link="linkedin.com/in/bennett-pohlmann/" />
        <Social name="instagram" link="instagram.com/toaster6161/" />
        <Social name="last.fm" link="last.fm/user/BEnh3N" />
