      </div>

      <H>projects</H>
      <p class="mb-8">to be filled in...</p>

      <H>this site</H>
      <p>
        This site is mainly to be used as a personal portfolio and a place to
        <Link url="/blog">write about my experiences</Link> with life and technology.
        <br />
        Big inspiration for this site came from
        <Link url="https://basicappleguy.com">Basic Apple Guy</Link>,
        <Link url="https://jamesbvaughan.com">James Vaughan</Link>, and
        <Link url="https://cobalt.tools">cobalt</Link>. The typing effect on the
        home screen was ripped directly from
        <Link url="https://bun.sh">Bun's homepage</Link>.
        <br />
        I plan on writing a blog post further down the line detailing more about
        the technology behind this site.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
